{"tid":2138402,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"球蠎擅闖民居浴室 嚇親寵物小烏龜兼失禁","createTime":"2020-08-03T14:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T15:01:50.000Z","uid":59684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"486931b49d20b3980ff1b3ae034ac0a5a4006a96","tid":2138402,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:18:27.000Z","msg":"旺角彌敦道780號麗英大廈，凌晨1時許，一條球蠎寵物蛇疑離開主人外逃，闖入大廈一住宅單位的浴室內，住客發現報警，警員到場召來蛇王協助，將擅闖民居的蠎蛇捉走，蠎蛇約2呎長。<br />\n蛇王表示，活捉蠎蛇期間，浴室內有一隻烏龜，烏龜疑受驚被蠎蛇嚇至失禁，該條球蠎約2歲大，一般作寵物飼養，相信球蠎是主人家中走失。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200714/HSWPG4YYOD3H3YSCBDTTXSTNRM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200714%2FHSWPG4YYOD3H3YSCBDTTXSTNRM%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=ad3efa93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200714%2FHSWPG4YYOD3H3YSCBDTTXSTNRM%2F&h=a8ab27c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200714/HSWPG4YYOD3H3YSCBDTTXSTNRM/</a><br />\n想睇烏龜瀨屎圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd827e2a4d6c7416e093ea7bd84cd1762c0537d","tid":2138402,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459f0dd128b9ecfb899ec956f874c02c0791ad9f","tid":2138402,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBzEC9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBzEC9p.jpg&h=cd224589&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8cba73272a2cedc8ffdf8f931e5a0e1ab7ab835","tid":2138402,"uid":364053,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"烏龜好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wa